data.description: This property is a diamond in the rough for those willing to roll up their sleeves. With some elbow grease and a keen eye for design, this house has the potential to become the perfect family home or a lucrative investment! Enjoy the giant lower level-perfect for entertaining or relaxing by the cozy fireplace. Large, fenced yard+patio provides all the space you need for yard games, more entertaining or grilling on your patio behind the privacy fence. Located in sought-after Maple Grove schools within walking distance to Basswood Elementary. Oversized 2 car garage with heater! New roof in 2020. Schedule your private tour today!
